<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="807">Note:</emphasis>
Ball (in 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="807">Feddes Repert.</emphasis>
69: 6. 1964) noted 10.1 (LINN) from Gotland, and therefore concluded it to be the diploid 
<typeStatus>cytotype</typeStatus>
